  "description": "This individual is a human sea-captain of middle years, broad-shouldered and compactly powerful in build, with bronze skin weathered by salt and sun. Brown eyes sit deep beneath pronounced brows, and a black hairstyle worn in a parted line frames a face marked by a broken nose set long ago. The jaw carries a permanent tension and the hands bear thickened callus lines typical of rope-work and shipboard labor. A thin pale seam crosses the lower lip, leaving a slight asymmetry that has become a defining feature.",
